       Race : Dwarf
      Stats : Strength     24
              Constitution 21
              Dexterity    15
              Wisdom       13
              Intelligence 13
              Charisma     14
  Eye Sight : very good
Description : Dwarves are typically workers in mines.  They have some
              of the best eyes in the realm.  Dwarves are also some of
              the strongest and hairiest people in the realm.  No one 
              really knows the colour of a dwarf's skin since they 
              seldome bath.
Occupations : Dwarves make very good fighters.  Although weaker then 
              giants they are much more agile and can manouver in ways
              and places giants can not.  Their higher wisdom helps 
              against magic users too.
